=============
python-recsys
=============

A python library for implementing a recommender system.  Originally written by ocelma, forked by delvv.

==================
INSTALLATION NOTES
==================

1) Just run:

   pip install python-recsys

..and you're all set!

2) Dependencies

python-recsys is build on top of Divisi2, with csc-pysparse (Divisi2 also requires NumPy, and uses Networkx).
python-recsys also requires SciPy.

If you have any issues with installation (above), you can manually install the dependencies:

    sudo apt-get install python-scipy
    sudo apt-get install python-numpy
    sudo pip install csc-pysparse networkx divisi2

